snippet.title: Best VGM 759 - Mario & Luigi : Partners in Time - Thwomp Volcano
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 443 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KnTyM5OmRAM
Best VGM 2205 - https://youtu.be/TSVG-cKj71Y


A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Mario & Luigi: Partners in Time (2005)
Thwomp Volcano
Yoko Shimomura
